OL,6,FA Tewkesbury couple say they're having
OL,7,Fto cuddle their dogs to keep warm at
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,FJohn and Wenefreda Dockree first
OL,11,Fturned on their heating in November
OL,12,Fwhen snow arrived. However, just an
OL,13,Fhour later they turned it off because
OL,14,Fthey can't afford the bills now
OL,15,Fthey've lost their winter fuel payment.
OL,17,FThe 73-year-old veteran said: "If I
OL,18,Fhave to put the heating on more than
OL,19,Fwe are doing now, we're going to have
OL,20,Fto cut back on food.
