OL,6,F"What can I do? I don't want to get
OL,7,Fmyself into debt. I can't afford to
OL,8,Fget myself into debt."
OL,10,FThe couple have two rescue dogs, which
OL,11,Fthey say keep them warm at night.
OL,13,FJohn said: "They jump up on the bed,
OL,14,Fand you can feel the warmth come from
OL,15,Fthem, and that's a good thing because
OL,16,Fthey love us."
OL,18,FLast summer Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,19,Fannounced the winter fuel benefit of
OL,20,Fup to #300 would be removed for many
OL,21,Fpeople to save #1.4bn per year.
