OL,6,FPreviously all pensioners received a
OL,7,Flump sum of between #200 and #300 to
OL,8,Fhelp with energy bills, but now the
OL,9,Fpayment is available only to those on
OL,10,Fpension credit who have an income
OL,11,Fbelow #218.15 per week as a single
OL,12,Fperson, or #332.95 as a couple.
OL,14,FSince the announcement, applications
OL,15,Ffor pension credit have increased by
OL,16,F145%.
