OL,6,FFor John, pension credit is not an
OL,7,Foption. His state pension of #213.50
OL,8,Fper week together plus his wife's
OL,9,Fincome from cleaning offices for two
OL,10,Fhours, five days a week leaves their
OL,11,Fincome #2 above the threshold of
OL,12,Feligibility.
OL,14,FThe lack of heat has also had an
OL,15,Fimpact on their house. Existing damp
OL,16,Fproblems have worsened and black mould
OL,17,Fnow covers large areas of the house,
OL,18,Fcausing John additional worries about
OL,19,Ftheir health.
