OL,6,FThe NHS recommends homes should be at
OL,7,Fleast 18 degrees to lower the risk of
OL,8,Fheart attacks, strokes, breathing
OL,9,Fproblems and respiratory illnesses.
OL,11,FJohn said: "I'm ashamed to say I'm
OL,12,FBritish, from the way I'm being
OL,13,Ftreated at the moment.
OL,15,F"I did my bit in the army for this
OL,16,Fcountry, and I now I wonder what for."
OL,18,FThe Chancellor has said her "tough
OL,19,Fchoice" will put public finances on a
OL,20,F"firmer footing".
